qO0w6BtA">Kỳ 7 - 其七</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-H%C3%A0m/author-FUm0aTv6MMEhKSvKSGMoVA">Vũ Phạm Hàm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/L%C3%A3o-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-h%C3%A0nh/poem-q9t4hdGxFPoZsjF0pTYb4w">Lão tướng hành - 老將行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Phong-t%E1%BA%ADt-chu-trung-ph%E1%BB%A5c-ch%E1%BA%A9m-th%C6%B0-ho%C3%A0i-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-l%E1%BB%A5c-v%E1%BA%ADn-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-tr%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BB%93-Nam-th%C3%A2n-h%E1%BB%AFu/poem-maRxAMOCboIbSdvxXl781Q">Phong tật chu trung phục chẩm thư hoài tam thập lục vận, phụng trình Hồ Nam thân hữu - 風疾舟中伏枕書懷三十六韻，奉呈湖南親友</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Ho%C3%A0n/Th%E1%BB%8B-bi%E1%BB%83u-%C4%91%E1%BB%87/poem-T3edrFVOA7yHmRBQ0edzZQ">Thị biểu đệ - 示表弟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Ho%C3%A0n/author-hAMSURaiVBULjeOhr37mnQ">Phan Ngọc Hoàn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Nguy%C3%AAn-H%C3%A0nh/Thu-t%E1%BB%A9/poem-vIvMcpRr55FhTbL7z_5IFw">Thu tứ - 秋思</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Nguy%C3%AAn-H%C3%A0nh/author-xb9f8XgZhtsCrJqig5eRWg">Vũ Nguyên Hành</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
